    <div>
        <p>To personalise a page with data from their CRM, customers needed to add “tokens” to their templates. Typed with curly brackets (like ), these tokens were impossible to discover and understand as functionality, often unclear what the original CRM references were, and even if they did, prone to typos. I needed to redesign how tokens worked, support creating from more data sources, so customers never had to leave their CRM.</p>
